            "html": "Members of this battle-yak-mounted troop are equipped with <i>+1 full plate</i>, <i>+1 lances</i>, <i>+1 composite longbows</i> (+4 Str) with 20 arrows, and gory trophies of past victories. Their yzobu mounts (<i>Pathfinder RPG Monster Codex</i> 124) wear military saddles and chain barding."
